Ramen:
- Ramen noodles
- Broth (chicken, pork, miso, etc.)
- Protein (chicken, pork, tofu, etc.)
- Vegetables (seaweed, mushrooms, scallions, etc.)
- Egg (soft-boiled or poached)
- Soy sauce or miso paste (for flavor)
- Sesame oil (for flavor)
- Optional: Nori sheets, sesame seeds, chili oil (for garnish)
